Classification: Scripted
Genre: Comedy | Drama | Family
Status: New Series
Network: Sky One ( United Kingdom)

Starlings is a comedy drama serries broadcast on Sky One. The series stars Brendan Coyle and Lesley Sharp.The Starling family make way for a new addition to their already-hectic family when granddad moves in. The series is co-written by Matt King and Steve Edge and produced by Steve Coogan and Henry Normal.
